{
  "texts": [
    "This allows for more complex, multimodal reasoning tasks.",
    "PathVQA is specific to pathology images, such as histopathological slides, and is valuable for disease diagnosis in pathology using VQA techniques.U-Xray, CheXpert, PadChest, and MIMIC-CXR focus on chest X-ray classification and segmentation.",
    "These datasets are widely used in developing models for automatic disease detection (e.g., pneumonia, pneumothorax) and diagnosis from X-rays.",
    "CheXpert, with over 224,000 labeled images, provides precise annotations for several lung diseases, making it a benchmark for chest disease classification.",
    "PadChest contains over 160,000 labeled images and expands its scope with Spanish-language reports, contributing to multilingual model training."
  ]
}